---
By: Srimad Bhagavatam
Source:
  ID: 57c5499b-c3b2-4b09-92a9-a6e977a32050
  Locus:
    Page: 189
    Verse: 16
Tags:
  - God
---
The eternal, unchangeable Lord, who is formless and attributeless, who is
absolute knowledge and absolute bliss, evolves the whole universe out of
Himself, plays with it, and again withdraws it into Himself.
